#### 2. **Advanced Text Formatting**
Full support for **rich formatting** that maintains consistency:

- **Bold text** for important elements
- *Italic text* for subtle emphasis
- `Inline code` for technical references
- ==Highlighted text== to call out critical information
- ~~Strikethrough text~~ to show changes
- [Working links](https://contentos.pro) with standard formatting

